1. to find the area of a triangle:

base=10
height=5
area=1/2*(base*height)
print("Area of a triangle is:",area)



2.)Write a program that asks user to enter a number. Program should then tell if number is odd or even.

indian=["samosa","Idly","Paratta"]
Chinese=["Fried rice","Rolls","Dumplings"]
Italian=["Pizza","Pasta"]

dish=input("Enter dish name:")
if dish in indian:
  print("Indian dish")
elif dish in Chinese:
  print("Chinese")
elif dish in Italian:
  print("Italian")
 else
  print("other cuisine:",dish)
